# Bookkeeping standards

## Method

- Default: **accrual basis** per company settings.
- Double-entry implied in dashboard summaries (assets = liabilities + equity).

## Financial snapshots

- `app/src/lib/financials.ts` builds cash flow, balance sheet, and income detail from Supabase.
- Payroll: separate employee withholdings from employer contributions.

## Reconciliation

- Match invoice totals to payments monthly in the app.
- Expenses: mark `paid` when cleared against bank.
- Unmatched items >30 days → flag for owner review.

## Capitalization

- Expense items under **$500** unless part of a single asset or clear long-life item.
- Ambiguous → log in `company/decision-log.md` and ask owner.

## Reports

- Dashboard provides cumulative management P&L and balance sheet.
- Export or snapshot externally for CPA packages; do not commit private exports to git.
